address: 51 Kensington Church Street, London W8 4BA, United Kingdom
author: Kristin B.
description: We really liked this place a lot, Fiona was very personable as was her server. We were walk ins with not having "booked" a table yet she accommodated our party of 3. She made a tequila cocktail she called "summer in a glass" which was very refreshing. We had steak, spiraled sweet potato pasta, chicken Kiev which was a big hit. A yummy green salad shared with fresh parmesan dressing!
